{"tid":2364069,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普批彈劾行動荒謬至極已造成極大憤怒：「我不希望出現暴力」","createTime":"2021-01-12T16:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T16:50:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a357bc5e7b69fa4c352fb6b6d015e99a1bb2a4","tid":2364069,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普今天表示，國會準備彈劾他實是「荒謬至極」，這已經造成「極大憤怒」。他並強調自己不希望出現暴力。<br />\n<br />\n川普要登上「陸戰隊一號」（Marine One）直升機準備啟程前往德州時說，國會眾議院推動在13日對他提出彈劾案，堪稱是「政治史上最大獵巫行動的延續」。<br />\n<br />\n他告訴記者：「我不希望出現暴力。」<br />\n<br />\n這是川普自去年12月8日以來首度對記者發表談話，他沒有回應有關他是否會辭職的問題。<br />\n<br />\n川普將前往德州阿拉莫（Alamo），造訪自己的指標政績─邊界圍牆。這是支持他的抗議者6日闖入國會大廈的事件後，他首次公開露面。<br />\n<br />\n川普任內一直試圖減少跨境和合法移民人數，這項邊界圍牆計畫可追溯至他2016年許下的承諾。當年他誓言將建一道圍牆封鎖邊界。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202101120359.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202101120359.aspx&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEYpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=90d431ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202101120359.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"352a63e0d235c0104dcc029a9d20d1ef8a00cdab","tid":2364069,"uid":324629,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"唔想出現暴力就做嘢啦"},{"pid":"4f2304f5aea647fdfe42335b4830f0bf8b69df1a","tid":2364069,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"352a63e0d235c0104dcc029a9d20d1ef8a00cdab","tid":2364069,"uid":324629,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"唔想出現暴力就做嘢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"點解咁多人唔知總統國內冇乜能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d3a1a8daac7a27888282be7176cd50ffab80ed","tid":2364069,"uid":209890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQyA3LT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQyA3LT.